column2: Question

If the special election for the U.S. House of Representatives were being held today and the candidates were  Jon Ossoff, the Democrat and Karen Handel, the Republican, for whom would you vote, lean toward or have voted for?
Will Jon Ossoff's residence outside of the 6th Congressional District borders be a major factor in your vote, a minor factor or not a factor?
Will Karen Handel's lack of a college degree be a major factor in your vote, a minor factor or not a factor?
Will one reason for your vote for congress be to express support for President Trump, opposition to President Trump, or is President Trump not a factor in your choice?

If a candidate for U.S. congress has experience in public elected office, would that make you more likely to support that candidate,  more likely to oppose that candidate or wouldn't it make much difference in your vote?
How important will the issue of healthcare be in your vote?
How important will the issue of taxes be in your vote?
how important will the issue of traffic and transportation be in your vote?
How important will the issue of abortion be in your vote?
How important will the issue of government spending be in your vote?
Have you personally been contacted by a representative of the Ossoff campaign in-person asking you for your support, or not?
Have you personally been contacted by a representative of the Handel campaign in-person asking you for your support, or not?
Have in person phone calls or visits from campaign volunteers influenced your decision to vote for a candidate in the upcoming election?
How much did in person phone calls or visits from campaign volunteers influence your decision?
Have campaign ads influenced your decision to vote for a candidate in the upcoming election?
How much did campaign ads influence your decision?
Have endorsements influenced your decision to vote for a candidate in the upcoming election?
How much did endorsements influence your decision?
Have the opinions of friends and neighbors influenced your decision to vote for a candidate in the upcoming election?
How much did the opinions of friends and neighbors influence your decision?
Do you feel the special election is more important than past elections, less important or as important as past elections?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of Donald Trump?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of Mike Pence?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of Karen Handel?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of Jon Ossoff?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of the Democratic Party?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of the Republican Party?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of Nancy Pelosi?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of the House GOP Obamacare replacement bill?
Do you think things in this country are generally going in the right direction or do you feel things have gotten pretty seriously off on the wrong track?
How concerned are you about healthcare costs?
